values:
hmm.. it's been quite a while...
i'm not supposed to be on here though...
comp's on the frits... i hate viruses...
well... just wanted the couple ppl that read this to know that i'm doing ok...
sort of anywayz...
i would go into details, but one person who reads this' father is brothers with someone that i despise at this moment...
but NO ONE but the ppl who read this is to know that...
(eh hem... i.e. diana is not to tell her father that i hate my dad)
got it? good! anywayz...
i'm bored, and i should be typing a lab report... or in bed...
so i will go to bed becuz hw sucks...
byebyez...

p.s. 9 days til my bday!!!!!!!

back to school...
the show on new years was fucking, yes, i am going to use the real word this time, 
FUCKING AWESOME!!!!!
it was soo much fun!...
i can't wait til the next one...
hmm... homework awaits...

woot woot!!
new years eve show tonight!!
i can't wait!
bleeding through, saosin, scary kids scaring kids...
a heavenly mix + many more bands i might add...
i love life...
yesterday was better than tonight is going to be though...

well... it's been a long day...
merry jesus day by the way...
(hey, i rhymed)...
well... my xmas continues tomorrow...
so i have to get a good night's sleep...
night night my little darlings...
(hi diana... cuz ur the only one who reads this...)
i hate christmas... i don't want to go anywhere... i want to see my joe... i'm bored too... i love this picture!!... merry xmas eve...!

went bowling tonight with youth group...
not that much fun, but w/e...
nothing else to report except i'm super worried right now...
(joe is driving home, and he's tired)...
well, gotta go wait for the phone call of safety...

i was fine earlier...
but now i'm a bit pissed off, and don't ask y...
it's a joe thing, and i wish it wasn't...
i love him soooo much, 
but, god, i wish i didn't get angry so easily...

so, the from first to last show last night was effing awesome!!
i'm bored today though, so call me or something...
i kinda want to go shopping...
hmmm...

i don't like being sad...
and plz don't ask me y becuz...
well, i don't want to tell you!

i'm sick...
i hate it sooo much!!
and i want to see joe!!
i never get to talk to him anymore...
anywayz,... i still have to do an essay that was actually due today,
so i'm gonna go do that...
goodnight... 



P.S. I WANT JOE!!!

the bus didn't come to get me this morning...
so i had to miss school... oh darn... haha
oh well, kelsey isn't at skool either, so it's ok...
lol, well, that's it... and
2 months and 5 days til my bday...
the countdown has begun... lol

i'm bored...
my behind the wheel on sunday went good...
i didn't hurt anyone or anything like that!!
i was driving with my mom to walmart today...
haha... not far, but it's ok...
i got wings!!
call me ppls... i'm bored!!!

i have my first behind-the-wheel today...
i'm afraid...
i'm gonna crash or something...
ahhhhhh!!!
but last night helped to relax me... haha

i'm sooo tired!!
i had a long night of making chocolate with aaron...
it was fun!
i should make chocolate more often!
oh, and for those of u who haven't yet heard...
i cut my hair!
well... goodnight and sweet dreams...
Zzz...

went to the game...
and strangely, the dance...
it was actually fun...
can u imagine me dancing...?
hmm...

the concert was FUCKING AWESOME!!!!!!!!
and yet...
i am horribly depressed right now...

so... greg is here from vegas... he was suposed to stay only til tomorrow... but now he is here til sunday... joe came over tonight to meet him... it went good... it think... TWO MORE DAYS!!!! i can't wait!! i can't think of anything else... so goodnight...

i've been at kelsey's house all week
becuz my mom and bernie were on a cruise...
and i didn't want to stay with my dad...
and last night my dad and layla and i had a huge fight...
and i am no longer going over there...
ever!
but i did get to see joe this weekend!
i was so so so so happy about that at least...
and hopefully we get to see each other this week some time...
(hint hint)...
well... i'm going to go eat cuz i'm very hungry...
call me

it's finally friday, 
but i can't see joe this weekend...
or next weekend probably...
3 weeks is a very long time...
i hate life...
i can't go on like this...
i'm sooo glad that joe is getting his license soon!
i'm gonna go sit...
and be bored...
call me if u wanna do something tonight...
or tomorrow for that matter...
ttyl, byebye...

an okay day...
wonderful: got to see joe,
but not so wonderful: family was here...
i got my hairs cut though...
don't worry joe...
it's not shorter...
it was only like an inch...
i am soooo tired,
and i have church in the morning...
bleh...
i hope i get to see joe tomorrow...
if i don't i might die...
i'm going to bed now...
night everyone...

no short day...
but at least i get to see joe tomorrow!
i can't wait...
i haven't seen him in like a week,
but it feels like an eternity...
i'll be totally bored tonight,
so if anyone wants to do anything...
i'm here...
call me if u want to go somewhere...

yay for 2 minimum days in a row...
but only becuz half the classes at skool don't have light...
haha, the power went out last night...
during back to skool night while all the parents were there...
this was the best week ever...
hopefully another short day tomorrow...?

bleh...
i'm sick...
and depressed...
could it get worse...?

no school today...
saw the 40-year-old virgin with joe...
bored as hell right now becuz joe just left...
i don't want to go to skool tomorrow...
it's gonna suck...
more and more homework...
gonna go take a shower and go to bed i suppose...
bleh... i hate life...
